Ghum Hai Kisikey Pyaar Meiin (transl. Lost in Someone's Love) is an Indian Hindi-language television drama series that premiered on 5 October 2020 on Star Plus. It is also digitally available on Disney+ Hotstar. It stars Ayesha Singh, Neil Bhatt and Aishwarya Sharma Bhatt. Produced by Cockrow Entertainment and Shaika Films, it is a loose adaptation of Star Jalsha's Kusum Dola.
